{
  "video_id": "piCQ3_tcRUQ",
  "title": "Why statistics are fascinating: the numbers are us | Alan Smith | TEDxExeter",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12534.0,
      "end_time": 15654.0,
      "text": "Back in 2003,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15654.0,
      "end_time": 19314.0,
      "text": "the UK government carried out a survey."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19314.0,
      "end_time": 22487.0,
      "text": "And it was a survey that measured levels of numeracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22487.0,
      "end_time": 23748.0,
      "text": "in the population."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23748.0,
      "end_time": 25415.0,
      "text": "And they were shocked to find out"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25415.0,
      "end_time": 28803.0,
      "text": "that for every 100 working age adults in the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28803.0,
      "end_time": 32712.0,
      "text": "47 of them lacked Level 1 numeracy skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32712.000000000004,
      "end_time": 37230.0,
      "text": "Now, Level 1 numeracy skills -- that&#39;s low-end GCSE score."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37230.0,
      "end_time": 40502.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the ability to deal with fractions, percentages and decimals."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40502.0,
      "end_time": 45154.0,
      "text": "So this figure prompted a lot of hand-wringing in Whitehall."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45154.0,
      "end_time": 46806.0,
      "text": "Policies were changed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46806.0,
      "end_time": 48552.0,
      "text": "investments were made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48552.0,
      "end_time": 51614.0,
      "text": "and then they ran the survey again in 2011."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51614.0,
      "end_time": 55841.0,
      "text": "So can you guess what happened to this number?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55841.0,
      "end_time": 57309.0,
      "text": "It went up to 49."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57309.0,
      "end_time": 58782.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58782.0,
      "end_time": 61255.0,
      "text": "And in fact, when I reported this figure in the FT,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61255.0,
      "end_time": 62950.0,
      "text": "one of our readers joked and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62950.0,
      "end_time": 66735.0,
      "text": "&quot;This figure is only shocking to 51 percent of the population.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66735.0,
      "end_time": 69045.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69045.0,
      "end_time": 72226.0,
      "text": "But I preferred, actually, the reaction of a schoolchild"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72226.0,
      "end_time": 75345.0,
      "text": "when I presented at a school this information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75345.0,
      "end_time": 76900.0,
      "text": "who raised their hand and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76900.0,
      "end_time": 79440.0,
      "text": "&quot;How do we know that the person who made that number"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79440.0,
      "end_time": 81279.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t one of the 49 percent either?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81279.0,
      "end_time": 82557.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82557.0,
      "end_time": 86631.0,
      "text": "So clearly, there&#39;s a numeracy issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86631.0,
      "end_time": 88765.0,
      "text": "because these are important skills for life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88765.0,
      "end_time": 92656.0,
      "text": "and a lot of the changes that we want to introduce in this century"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 92656.0,
      "end_time": 95121.0,
      "text": "involve us becoming more comfortable with numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95121.0,
      "end_time": 96993.0,
      "text": "Now, it&#39;s not just an English problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96993.0,
      "end_time": 101947.0,
      "text": "OECD this year released some figures looking at numeracy in young people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101947.0,
      "end_time": 104751.0,
      "text": "and leading the way, the USA --"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104751.0,
      "end_time": 109445.0,
      "text": "nearly 40 percent of young people in the US have low numeracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109445.0,
      "end_time": 110766.0,
      "text": "Now, England is there too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110766.0,
      "end_time": 115923.0,
      "text": "but there are seven OECD countries with figures above 20 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115923.0,
      "end_time": 118706.0,
      "text": "That is a problem, because it doesn&#39;t have to be that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118706.0,
      "end_time": 120738.0,
      "text": "If you look at the far end of this graph,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120738.0,
      "end_time": 124122.0,
      "text": "you can see the Netherlands and Korea are in single figures."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124122.0,
      "end_time": 128530.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s definitely a numeracy problem that we want to address."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 128530.0,
      "end_time": 131484.0,
      "text": "Now, as useful as studies like these are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 131484.0,
      "end_time": 136908.0,
      "text": "I think we risk herding people inadvertently into one of two categories;"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136908.0,
      "end_time": 138708.0,
      "text": "that there are two kinds of people:"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 138708.0,
      "end_time": 143081.0,
      "text": "those people that are comfortable with numbers, that can do numbers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143081.0,
      "end_time": 145341.0,
      "text": "and the people who can&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 145341.0,
      "end_time": 147466.0,
      "text": "And what I&#39;m trying to talk about here today"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 147466.0,
      "end_time": 150532.0,
      "text": "is to say that I believe that is a false dichotomy."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150532.0,
      "end_time": 152424.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not an immutable pairing."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 152424.0,
      "end_time": 156096.0,
      "text": "I think you don&#39;t have to have tremendously high levels of numeracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 156096.0,
      "end_time": 157848.0,
      "text": "to be inspired by numbers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 157848.0,
      "end_time": 161407.0,
      "text": "and that should be the starting point to the journey ahead."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161407.0,
      "end_time": 165742.0,
      "text": "And one of the ways in which we can begin that journey, for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 165742.0,
      "end_time": 167492.0,
      "text": "is looking at statistics."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 167492.0,
      "end_time": 171011.0,
      "text": "Now, I am the first to acknowledge that statistics has got somewhat"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 171011.0,
      "end_time": 172353.0,
      "text": "of an image problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 172353.0,
      "end_time": 173424.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 173424.0,
      "end_time": 174980.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the part of mathematics"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174980.0,
      "end_time": 178063.0,
      "text": "that even mathematicians don&#39;t particularly like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 178063.0,
      "end_time": 182099.0,
      "text": "because whereas the rest of maths is all about precision and certainty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 182099.0,
      "end_time": 184813.0,
      "text": "statistics is almost the reverse of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 184813.0,
      "end_time": 189492.0,
      "text": "But actually, I was a late convert to the world of statistics myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 189492.0,
      "end_time": 191598.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;d asked my undergraduate professors"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 191598.0,
      "end_time": 196381.0,
      "text": "what two subjects would I be least likely to excel in after university,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 196381.0,
      "end_time": 199172.0,
      "text": "they&#39;d have told you statistics and computer programming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 199172.0,
      "end_time": 202135.0,
      "text": "and yet here I am, about to show you some statistical graphics"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 202135.0,
      "end_time": 203765.0,
      "text": "that I programmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 203765.0,
      "end_time": 205544.0,
      "text": "So what inspired that change in me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 205544.0,
      "end_time": 209216.0,
      "text": "What made me think that statistics was actually an interesting thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 209216.0,
      "end_time": 211889.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really because statistics are about us."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 211889.0,
      "end_time": 214495.0,
      "text": "If you look at the etymology of the word statistics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 214495.0,
      "end_time": 217128.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the science of dealing with data"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 217128.0,
      "end_time": 219582.0,
      "text": "about the state or the community that we live in."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 219582.0,
      "end_time": 222960.0,
      "text": "So statistics are about us as a group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222960.0,
      "end_time": 224659.0,
      "text": "not us as individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 224659.0,
      "end_time": 226153.0,
      "text": "And I think as social animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 226153.0,
      "end_time": 230121.0,
      "text": "we share this fascination about how we as individuals relate to our groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 230121.0,
      "end_time": 231533.0,
      "text": "to our peers."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 231533.0,
      "end_time": 234667.0,
      "text": "And statistics in this way are at their most powerful"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 234667.0,
      "end_time": 236497.0,
      "text": "when they surprise us."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 236497.0,
      "end_time": 239728.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s been some really wonderful surveys carried out recently"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 239728.0,
      "end_time": 241474.0,
      "text": "by Ipsos MORI in the last few years."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241474.0,
      "end_time": 244066.0,
      "text": "They did some really interesting stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 244066.0,
      "end_time": 246798.0,
      "text": "They did a survey of over 1,000 adults in the UK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 246798.0,
      "end_time": 251002.0,
      "text": "and said, for every 100 people in England and Wales,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 251002.0,
      "end_time": 253696.0,
      "text": "how many of them are Muslim?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253696.0,
      "end_time": 256366.0,
      "text": "Now the average answer from this survey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 256366.0,
      "end_time": 260264.0,
      "text": "which was supposed to be representative of the total population ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 260264.0,
      "end_time": 262802.0,
      "text": "was 24."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 262802.0,
      "end_time": 264202.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what people thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 264202.0,
      "end_time": 267865.0,
      "text": "British people think 24 out of every 100 people in the country are Muslim."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 267865.0,
      "end_time": 273252.0,
      "text": "Now, official figures reveal that figure to be about five."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 273252.0,
      "end_time": 277263.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s this big variation between what we think, our perception,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 277263.0,
      "end_time": 279325.0,
      "text": "and the reality as given by statistics."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 279325.0,
      "end_time": 280893.0,
      "text": "And I think that&#39;s interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 280893.0,
      "end_time": 284732.0,
      "text": "What could possibly be causing that misperception?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 284732.0,
      "end_time": 286610.0,
      "text": "And I was so thrilled with this study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 286610.0,
      "end_time": 290114.0,
      "text": "I started to take questions out in presentations. I was referring to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 290114.0,
      "end_time": 291356.0,
      "text": "Now, I did a presentation"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 291356.0,
      "end_time": 293690.0,
      "text": "at St. Paul&#39;s School for Girls in Hammersmith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 293690.0,
      "end_time": 295854.0,
      "text": "and I had an audience rather like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 295854.0,
      "end_time": 299746.0,
      "text": "except it was comprised entirely of sixth-form girls."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 299746.0,
      "end_time": 303018.0,
      "text": "And I said, &quot;Girls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 303018.0,
      "end_time": 307585.0,
      "text": "how many teenage girls do you think the British public think"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 307585.0,
      "end_time": 309357.0,
      "text": "get pregnant every year?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 309357.0,
      "end_time": 312873.0,
      "text": "And the girls were apoplectic when I said"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 312873.0,
      "end_time": 316810.0,
      "text": "the British public think that 15 out of every 100 teenage girls"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 316810.0,
      "end_time": 318849.0,
      "text": "get pregnant in the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 318849.0,
      "end_time": 321104.0,
      "text": "And they had every right to be angry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 321104.0,
      "end_time": 323886.0,
      "text": "because in fact, I&#39;d have to have closer to 200 dots"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 323886.0,
      "end_time": 325480.0,
      "text": "before I could color one in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 325480.0,
      "end_time": 328019.0,
      "text": "in terms of what the official figures tell us."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 328019.0,
      "end_time": 331843.0,
      "text": "And rather like numeracy, this is not just an English problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 331843.0,
      "end_time": 336871.0,
      "text": "Ipsos MORI expanded the survey in recent years to go across the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 336871.0,
      "end_time": 340145.0,
      "text": "And so, they asked Saudi Arabians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 340145.0,
      "end_time": 342690.0,
      "text": "for every 100 adults in your country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 342690.0,
      "end_time": 346746.0,
      "text": "how many of them are overweight or obese?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 346746.0,
      "end_time": 352622.0,
      "text": "And the average answer from the Saudis was just over a quarter."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 352622.0,
      "end_time": 353848.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what they thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 353848.0,
      "end_time": 356440.0,
      "text": "Just over a quarter of adults are overweight or obese."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 356440.0,
      "end_time": 361245.0,
      "text": "The official figures show, actually, it&#39;s nearer to three-quarters."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 361245.0,
      "end_time": 362725.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 362725.0,
      "end_time": 365041.0,
      "text": "So again, a big variation."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 365041.0,
      "end_time": 369511.0,
      "text": "And I love this one: they asked in Japan, they asked the Japanese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 369511.0,
      "end_time": 371495.0,
      "text": "for every 100 Japanese people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 371495.0,
      "end_time": 374741.0,
      "text": "how many of them live in rural areas?"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 374741.0,
      "end_time": 379666.0,
      "text": "The average was about a 50-50 split, just over halfway."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 379666.0,
      "end_time": 383837.0,
      "text": "They thought 56 out of every 100 Japanese people lived in rural areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 383837.0,
      "end_time": 387179.0,
      "text": "The official figure is seven."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 387179.0,
      "end_time": 391653.0,
      "text": "So extraordinary variations, and surprising to some,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 391653.0,
      "end_time": 394066.0,
      "text": "but not surprising to people who have read the work"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 394066.0,
      "end_time": 398482.0,
      "text": "of Daniel Kahneman, for example, the Nobel-winning economist."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 398482.0,
      "end_time": 403598.0,
      "text": "He and his colleague, Amos Tversky, spent years researching this disjoint"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 403598.0,
      "end_time": 406767.0,
      "text": "between what people perceive and the reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 406767.0,
      "end_time": 410542.0,
      "text": "the fact that people are actually pretty poor intuitive statisticians."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 410542.0,
      "end_time": 412326.0,
      "text": "And there are many reasons for this."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 412326.0,
      "end_time": 415465.0,
      "text": "Individual experiences, certainly, can influence our perceptions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 415465.0,
      "end_time": 419447.0,
      "text": "but so, too, can things like the media reporting things by exception,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 419447.0,
      "end_time": 422475.0,
      "text": "rather than what&#39;s normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 422475.0,
      "end_time": 424625.0,
      "text": "Kahneman had a nice way of referring to that."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 424625.0,
      "end_time": 426734.0,
      "text": "He said, &quot;We can be blind to the obvious&quot; --"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 426734.0,
      "end_time": 428396.0,
      "text": "so we&#39;ve got the numbers wrong --"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 428396.0,
      "end_time": 430742.0,
      "text": "&quot;but we can be blind to our blindness about it.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 430742.0,
      "end_time": 435432.0,
      "text": "And that has enormous repercussions for decision making."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 435432.0,
      "end_time": 438308.0,
      "text": "So at the statistics office while this was all going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 438308.0,
      "end_time": 440244.0,
      "text": "I thought this was really interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 440244.0,
      "end_time": 442278.0,
      "text": "I said, this is clearly a global problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 442278.0,
      "end_time": 444737.0,
      "text": "but maybe geography is the issue here."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 444737.0,
      "end_time": 448670.0,
      "text": "These were questions that were all about, how well do you know your country?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 448670.0,
      "end_time": 452687.0,
      "text": "So in this case, it&#39;s how well do you know 64 million people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 452687.0,
      "end_time": 455443.0,
      "text": "Not very well, it turns out. I can&#39;t do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 455443.0,
      "end_time": 456791.0,
      "text": "So I had an idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 456791.0,
      "end_time": 459938.0,
      "text": "which was to think about this same sort of approach"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 459938.0,
      "end_time": 462067.0,
      "text": "but to think about it in a very local sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 462067.0,
      "end_time": 463282.0,
      "text": "Is this a local?"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 463282.0,
      "end_time": 465247.0,
      "text": "If we reframe the questions and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 465247.0,
      "end_time": 467893.0,
      "text": "how well do you know your local area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 467893.0,
      "end_time": 471337.0,
      "text": "would your answers be any more accurate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 471337.0,
      "end_time": 473123.0,
      "text": "So I devised a quiz:"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 473123.0,
      "end_time": 475974.0,
      "text": "How well do you know your area?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 475974.0,
      "end_time": 477887.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a simple Web app."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 477887.0,
      "end_time": 479094.0,
      "text": "You put in a post code"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 479094.0,
      "end_time": 481825.0,
      "text": "and then it will ask you questions based on census data"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 481825.0,
      "end_time": 483825.0,
      "text": "for your local area."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 483825.0,
      "end_time": 485972.0,
      "text": "And I was very conscious in designing this."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 485972.0,
      "end_time": 490105.0,
      "text": "I wanted to make it open to the widest possible range of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 490105.0,
      "end_time": 492957.0,
      "text": "not just the 49 percent who can get the numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 492957.0,
      "end_time": 494736.0,
      "text": "I wanted everyone to engage with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 494736.0,
      "end_time": 496685.0,
      "text": "So for the design of the quiz,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 496685.0,
      "end_time": 500324.0,
      "text": "I was inspired by the isotypes"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 500324.0,
      "end_time": 502950.0,
      "text": "of Otto Neurath from the 1920s and &#39;30s."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 502950.0,
      "end_time": 507822.0,
      "text": "Now, these are methods for representing numbers"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 507822.0,
      "end_time": 510060.0,
      "text": "using repeating icons."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 510060.0,
      "end_time": 513249.0,
      "text": "And the numbers are there, but they sit in the background."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 513249.0,
      "end_time": 515996.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a great way of representing quantity"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 515996.0,
      "end_time": 519004.0,
      "text": "without resorting to using terms like &quot;percentage,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 519004.0,
      "end_time": 520258.0,
      "text": "&quot;fractions&quot; and &quot;ratios.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 520258.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522730.00000000006,
      "text": "So here&#39;s the quiz."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 522730.0,
      "end_time": 524401.0,
      "text": "The layout of the quiz is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 524401.0,
      "end_time": 527244.0,
      "text": "you have your repeating icons on the left-hand side there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 527244.0,
      "end_time": 530391.0,
      "text": "and a map showing you the area we&#39;re asking you questions about"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 530391.0,
      "end_time": 531582.0,
      "text": "on the right-hand side."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 531582.0,
      "end_time": 532887.0,
      "text": "There are seven questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 532887.0,
      "end_time": 536804.0,
      "text": "Each question, there&#39;s a possible answer between zero and a hundred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 536804.0,
      "end_time": 538177.0,
      "text": "and at the end of the quiz,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 538177.0,
      "end_time": 541419.0,
      "text": "you get an overall score between zero and a hundred."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 541419.0,
      "end_time": 543527.0,
      "text": "And so because this is TEDxExeter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 543527.0,
      "end_time": 545876.0,
      "text": "I thought we would have a quick look at the quiz"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 545876.0,
      "end_time": 548209.0,
      "text": "for the first few questions of Exeter."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 548209.0,
      "end_time": 549638.0,
      "text": "And so the first question is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 549638.0,
      "end_time": 553204.0,
      "text": "For every 100 people, how many are aged under 16?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 553204.0,
      "end_time": 556828.0,
      "text": "Now, I don&#39;t know Exeter very well at all, so I had a guess at this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 556828.0,
      "end_time": 559413.0,
      "text": "but it gives you an idea of how this quiz works."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 559413.0,
      "end_time": 563143.0,
      "text": "You drag the slider to highlight your icons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 563143.0,
      "end_time": 565402.0,
      "text": "and then just click &quot;Submit&quot; to answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 565402.0,
      "end_time": 569089.0,
      "text": "and we animate away the difference between your answer and reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 569089.0,
      "end_time": 573569.0,
      "text": "And it turns out, I was a pretty terrible guess: five."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 573569.0,
      "end_time": 575017.0,
      "text": "How about the next question?"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 575017.0,
      "end_time": 577197.0,
      "text": "This is asking about what the average age is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 577197.0,
      "end_time": 579666.0,
      "text": "so the age at which half the population are younger"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 579666.0,
      "end_time": 581364.0,
      "text": "and half the population are older."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 581364.0,
      "end_time": 584738.0,
      "text": "And I thought 35 -- that sounds middle-aged to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 584738.0,
      "end_time": 588626.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 588626.0,
      "end_time": 590756.0,
      "text": "Actually, in Exeter, it&#39;s incredibly young,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 590756.0,
      "end_time": 595318.0,
      "text": "and I had underestimated the impact of the university in this area."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 595318.0,
      "end_time": 597373.0,
      "text": "The questions get harder as you go through."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 597373.0,
      "end_time": 600375.0,
      "text": "So this one&#39;s now asking about homeownership:"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 600375.0,
      "end_time": 604098.0,
      "text": "For every 100 households, how many are owned with a mortgage or loan?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 604098.0,
      "end_time": 605402.0,
      "text": "And I hedged my bets here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 605402.0,
      "end_time": 608524.0,
      "text": "because I didn&#39;t want to be more than 50 out on the answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 608524.0,
      "end_time": 610568.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 610568.0,
      "end_time": 613058.0,
      "text": "And actually, these get harder, these questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 613058.0,
      "end_time": 615941.0,
      "text": "because when you&#39;re in an area, when you&#39;re in a community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 615941.0,
      "end_time": 621215.0,
      "text": "things like age -- there are clues to whether a population is old or young."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 621215.0,
      "end_time": 623584.0,
      "text": "Just by looking around the area, you can see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 623584.0,
      "end_time": 626999.0,
      "text": "Something like homeownership is much more difficult to see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 626999.0,
      "end_time": 629631.0,
      "text": "so we revert to our own heuristics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 629631.0,
      "end_time": 634106.0,
      "text": "our own biases about how many people we think own their own homes."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 634106.0,
      "end_time": 637780.0,
      "text": "Now the truth is, when we published this quiz,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 637780.0,
      "end_time": 641341.0,
      "text": "the census data that it&#39;s based on was already a few years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 641341.0,
      "end_time": 645283.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve had online applications that allow you to put in a post code"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 645283.0,
      "end_time": 647521.0,
      "text": "and get statistics back for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 647521.0,
      "end_time": 648734.0,
      "text": "So in some senses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 648734.0,
      "end_time": 652307.0,
      "text": "this was all a little bit old and not necessarily new."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 652307.0,
      "end_time": 655970.0,
      "text": "But I was interested to see what reaction we might get"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 655970.0,
      "end_time": 658711.0,
      "text": "by gamifying the data in the way that we have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 658711.0,
      "end_time": 660142.0,
      "text": "by using animation"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 660142.0,
      "end_time": 665418.0,
      "text": "and playing on the fact that people have their own preconceptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 665418.0,
      "end_time": 670038.0,
      "text": "It turns out, the reaction was, um ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 670038.0,
      "end_time": 673230.0,
      "text": "was more than I could have hoped for."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 673230.0,
      "end_time": 676635.0,
      "text": "It was a long-held ambition of mine to bring down a statistics website"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 676635.0,
      "end_time": 678067.0,
      "text": "due to public demand."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 678067.0,
      "end_time": 679891.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 679891.0,
      "end_time": 683379.0,
      "text": "This URL contains the words &quot;statistics,&quot; &quot;gov&quot; and &quot;UK,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 683379.0,
      "end_time": 686645.0,
      "text": "which are three of people&#39;s least favorite words in a URL."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 686645.0,
      "end_time": 690654.0,
      "text": "And the amazing thing about this was that the website came down"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 690654.0,
      "end_time": 692771.0,
      "text": "at quarter to 10 at night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 692771.0,
      "end_time": 696006.0,
      "text": "because people were actually engaging with this data"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 696006.0,
      "end_time": 697569.0,
      "text": "of their own free will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 697569.0,
      "end_time": 699328.0,
      "text": "using their own personal time."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 699328.0,
      "end_time": 701339.0,
      "text": "I was very interested to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 701339.0,
      "end_time": 705076.0,
      "text": "that we got something like a quarter of a million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 705076.0,
      "end_time": 708372.0,
      "text": "playing the quiz within the space of 48 hours of launching it."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 708372.0,
      "end_time": 712323.0,
      "text": "And it sparked an enormous discussion online, on social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 712323.0,
      "end_time": 714448.0,
      "text": "which was largely dominated"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 714448.0,
      "end_time": 718401.0,
      "text": "by people having fun with their misconceptions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 718401.0,
      "end_time": 721484.0,
      "text": "which is something that I couldn&#39;t have hoped for any better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 721484.0,
      "end_time": 722668.0,
      "text": "in some respects."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 722668.0,
      "end_time": 725918.0,
      "text": "I also liked the fact that people started sending it to politicians."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 725918.0,
      "end_time": 728531.0,
      "text": "How well do you know the area you claim to represent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 728531.0,
      "end_time": 729717.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 729717.0,
      "end_time": 732172.0,
      "text": "And then just to finish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 732172.0,
      "end_time": 734526.0,
      "text": "going back to the two kinds of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 734526.0,
      "end_time": 736807.0,
      "text": "I thought it would be really interesting to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 736807.0,
      "end_time": 739646.0,
      "text": "how people who are good with numbers would do on this quiz."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 739646.0,
      "end_time": 742686.0,
      "text": "The national statistician of England and Wales, John Pullinger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 742686.0,
      "end_time": 745704.0,
      "text": "you would expect he would be pretty good."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 745704.0,
      "end_time": 748308.0,
      "text": "He got 44 for his own area."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 748308.0,
      "end_time": 750669.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 750669.0,
      "end_time": 755979.0,
      "text": "Jeremy Paxman -- admittedly, after a glass of wine ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 755979.0,
      "end_time": 757301.0,
      "text": "36."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 757301.0,
      "end_time": 758786.0,
      "text": "Even worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 758786.0,
      "end_time": 761572.0,
      "text": "It just shows you that the numbers can inspire us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 761572.0,
      "end_time": 762985.0,
      "text": "They can surprise us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 762985.0,
      "end_time": 765064.0,
      "text": "So very often, we talk about statistics"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 765064.0,
      "end_time": 767074.0,
      "text": "as being the science of uncertainty."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 767074.0,
      "end_time": 768881.0,
      "text": "My parting thought for today is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 768881.0,
      "end_time": 771941.0,
      "text": "actually, statistics is the science of us."
    },
    {
